o-short mapping. Implemented malicious URL detection and secure input validation to prevent unsafe link processing, enhancing user security by 95%. Optimized data storage using hash maps to achieve an average lookup time of O(1), increasing system memory efficiency by 30% and preventing link collisions.", "image_url": "/static/images/projects/url_shortener.png", "link": "https://github.com/Somineni-Venkata-Rajesh/URL-Shortener", "github_link": null, "is_live": true, "tags": "PHP, MySQL, HTML, CSS", "date": null}}, {"model": "app.project", "pk": 6, "fields": {"title": "Scientific Calculator", "description": "Designed and developed a fully functional Scientific Calculator featuring advanced mathematical capabilities including trigonometric, logarithmic, and square root functions. Created a modern, responsive UI using Glassmorphism design principles, incorporating a dynamic Light/Dark mode toggle and smooth CSS transitions for a premium user experience. Integrated interactive features such as a persistent calculation history log with pinning functionality and comprehensive keyboard support for efficient user input.", "image_url": "/static/images/projects/calculator.png", "link": "https://github.com/Somineni-Venkata-Rajesh/Calculator", "github_link": null, "is_live": true, "tags": "HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Glassmorphism, DOM API", "date": null}}, {"model": "app.project", "pk": 7, "fields": {"title": "FindStyle", "description": "Architected a multi-vendor e-commerce platform featuring a dual-user ecosystem with personalized dashboards for storefront management, global inventory, and revenue tracking\nEngineered complex business logic for dynamic product variants and multi-stage order tracking (Pending, Shipped, Delivered) with a secure, multi-method checkout process.\nIntegrated RESTful APIs for real-time pincode validation, verified-purchase reviews, and automated email notifications to enhance the end-to-end user experience.", "image_url": null, "link": null, "github_lin